Article 14 [Change of Privacy Policy]
① The company's personal information processing policy may change due to changes in the law and the company's internal policy.
In this case, the company shall notify the change on the company website or service at least 7 days prior to the effective date of the change.
It is notified in a way that users can check within. However, if the changed contents are unfavorable to the member or significant
In the case of a change in matters, we will notify you 30 days prior to the effective date
② We provide the previous version of the personal information processing policy so that users can easily check the changed contents.
Previous versions of the Privacy Policy can be viewed by clicking on the date in the upper right corner.
This privacy policy is effective from February 18, 2025.
